      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/kamil-al-ziyarat:2:65:10",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/24/2/65/10",
      "text": [
        " حَدَّثَنِي أَبُو خَلَّانَ [أَبُو فُلَانٍ] الْكِنْدِيُّ عَنْ أَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ (ع) قَالَ مَنْ أَتَى قَبْرَ الْحُسَيْنِ (ع) كَتَبَ اللَّهُ لَهُ حِجَّةً وَ عُمْرَةً"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayyid-mohsen-al-husayni-al-milani": [
          "10. My father narrated to me from Sa’d ibn ‘Abdillāh, from Ḥasan ibn ‘Ali Al-Kūfi, from ‘Abbās ibn ‘Āmir, from Abān ibn ‘Uthmān, from Abī Khallān Al-Kindi, who said: Abū ‘Abdillāh (Imam Sādiq (a.s.)) said: Allāh will register the reward of a Hajj and an ‘Umrah for those who go to (the Ziyārah of) the grave of Ḥusain (a.s.)."
        ]
      }
    },
